  <!-- EN: devourer -->
  <Devourer.label>吞噬兽</Devourer.label>
  <!-- EN: A massive monster with a gaping toothed maw and a stubby, snake-like body. The devourer can leap several times its body length to swallow a person whole. Powerful stomach acids rapidly digest the still-living victim. The remains are regurgitated soon after. -->
  <Devourer.description>拥有血盆大口以及粗壮蛇形身体的巨型怪物。吞噬兽能跃过数倍于身长的距离来将目标整个吞下。受害者往往还没咽气，就会被其强大的胃酸迅速消化。剩余的残骸很快就会被反刍出来。</Devourer.description>
  <!-- EN: Digesting {PAWN_nameDef}: {SECONDS} seconds left -->
  <Devourer.comps.CompDevourer.digestingInspector>正在消化{PAWN_nameDef}：剩余{SECONDS}秒</Devourer.comps.CompDevourer.digestingInspector>
  <!-- EN: A devourer swallowed {PAWN_nameDef} whole! Kill the devourer before it digests {PAWN_nameDef}. -->
  <Devourer.comps.CompDevourer.messageDigested>吞噬兽将{PAWN_nameDef}整个吞了下去！得赶在{PAWN_nameDef}被其消化前迅速击杀吞噬兽。</Devourer.comps.CompDevourer.messageDigested>
  <!-- EN: The devourer has regurgitated {PAWN_nameDef}. -->
  <Devourer.comps.CompDevourer.messageDigestionCompleted>吞噬兽反刍吐出了{PAWN_nameDef}的遗骸。</Devourer.comps.CompDevourer.messageDigestionCompleted>
  <!-- EN: {PAWN_nameDef} emerged from the devourer. -->
