  <!-- EN: nociosphere -->
  <Nociosphere.label>苦痛之球</Nociosphere.label>
  <!-- EN: A dark metallic sphere covered with curved and jagged grooves. The sphere emanates sensations of pain. It hurts to be near it.\n\nThe sphere thrums with a mysterious energy. It appears to be increasing in activity. It's not clear what will happen when it reaches its full capacity. However, if you capture it, you can decrease its activity by suppressing it. -->
  <Nociosphere.description>布满扭曲锯齿状凹槽的深色金属球体。该球体散发着痛苦的气息，靠近它就会感到疼痛。\n\n它放射出神秘的能量，且活动似乎越来越频繁。目前还不清楚当它完全激活时会发生什么。但假若将其捕获，就可以通过抑制它来降低其活跃度。</Nociosphere.description>
  <!-- EN: The nociosphere's activity level has reached 100% and it has activated. It has begun an onslaught of pain and destruction.\n\nIt will eventually depart - if you can survive long enough. -->
  <Nociosphere.comps.CompActivity.letterDesc>苦痛之球的活跃度已达到100%，它已完全激活，开始散布痛苦与毁灭。\n\n它最终将会离开，但前提是你能撑到那个时候。</Nociosphere.comps.CompActivity.letterDesc>
  <!-- EN: Nociosphere activated -->
  <Nociosphere.comps.CompActivity.letterTitle>苦痛之球已激活</Nociosphere.comps.CompActivity.letterTitle>
  <!-- EN: Nociosphere study progress -->
  <Nociosphere.comps.CompStudyUnlocks.studyNotes.0.label>苦痛之球调查有所进展</Nociosphere.comps.CompStudyUnlocks.studyNotes.0.label>
  <!-- EN: {PAWN_nameDef} has learned more about the inner workings of the nociosphere. It seems to have a single purpose - to inflict pain on those around it.\n\n{PAWN_nameDef} thinks {PAWN_pronoun} may be able to weaponize the nociosphere but you must study it more first. -->
  <Nociosphere.comps.CompStudyUnlocks.studyNotes.0.text>{PAWN_nameDef}已经对苦痛之球如何运作有了更多了解。它的存在似乎只有一个目的——给周围的个体带来痛苦。\n\n{PAWN_nameDef}认为{PAWN_pronoun}也许可以把苦痛之球用作武器，但必须先对它进行更多的调查。</Nociosphere.comps.CompStudyUnlocks.studyNotes.0.text>
  <!-- EN: Nociosphere study progress -->
  <Nociosphere.comps.CompStudyUnlocks.studyNotes.1.label>苦痛之球调查有所进展</Nociosphere.comps.CompStudyUnlocks.studyNotes.1.label>
  <!-- EN: By studying the nociosphere, you've learned how to intentionally activate it.\n\nWhen activated, the nociosphere will teleport to a remote location of your choice and unleash a barrage of pain on anyone nearby. The nociosphere will continue to hunt down anything nearby until it is destroyed or it chooses to return. Select the nociosphere to activate it. -->
  <Nociosphere.comps.CompStudyUnlocks.studyNotes.1.text>通过调查苦痛之球，你知晓了主动激活它的方式。\n\n激活后，苦痛之球会传送到你选择的偏远地点，并向附近的任何人释放无尽的痛苦。苦痛之球会继续追杀附近任何目标，直到其被摧毁或主动返回。选中苦痛之球以激活它。</Nociosphere.comps.CompStudyUnlocks.studyNotes.1.text>
  <!-- EN: Nociosphere study complete -->
  <Nociosphere.comps.CompStudyUnlocks.studyNotes.2.label>苦痛之球调查完成</Nociosphere.comps.CompStudyUnlocks.studyNotes.2.label>
  <!-- EN: {PAWN_nameDef} has made an alarming discovery about the nociosphere. The entity is showing early signs of instability.\n\nOnce the nociosphere starts to become unstable, you can dispose of it by sending it to attack a hostile threat. For a short period, the nociosphere will hunt down anything nearby - friend or foe.\n\nOnce its onslaught is complete, it will permanently depart. If it becomes fully unstable, it will no longer respond to suppression. -->
  <Nociosphere.comps.CompStudyUnlocks.studyNotes.2.text>对苦痛之球的调查让{PAWN_nameDef}有了惊人的发现。该实体显示出一些失控的早期迹象。\n\n当苦痛之球开始变得不稳定时，你可以将苦痛之球送去攻击敌对派系以放逐它。一段时间内，他会不分敌友攻击周遭一切，直到攻击结束，它便会永久离开。一旦其完全失控，将无法再被抑制。</Nociosphere.comps.CompStudyUnlocks.studyNotes.2.text>
  <!-- EN: Teleport the nociosphere to a nearby location. It will then unleash an onslaught of murder and pain on everyone nearby for a short time. The nociosphere will hunt down any creature, including allies and other entities.\n\nThe nociosphere can be sent multiple times. -->
  <Nociosphere.comps.CompNociosphere.activateDescString>将苦痛之球传送到附近地点。它将在短时间内对附近的所有目标发动杀戮、释放痛苦。苦痛之球会追杀包括友方单位与其他实体在内的所有目标。\n\n苦痛之球可以多次传送。</Nociosphere.comps.CompNociosphere.activateDescString>
  <!-- EN: Send the nociosphere... -->
  <Nociosphere.comps.CompNociosphere.activateLabelString>派遣苦痛之球</Nociosphere.comps.CompNociosphere.activateLabelString>
  <!-- EN: sending {0}: {1}s -->
  <Nociosphere.comps.CompNociosphere.activatingString>正在派遣{0}：{1}秒</Nociosphere.comps.CompNociosphere.activatingString>
  <!-- EN: Becoming unstable -->
  <Nociosphere.comps.CompNociosphere.becomingUnstableInspectText>开始不稳定</Nociosphere.comps.CompNociosphere.becomingUnstableInspectText>
  <!-- EN: The nociosphere is departing. -->
  <Nociosphere.comps.CompNociosphere.departingMessage>苦痛之球正在离开</Nociosphere.comps.CompNociosphere.departingMessage>
  <!-- EN: send nociosphere -->
  <Nociosphere.comps.CompNociosphere.jobString>派遣苦痛之球</Nociosphere.comps.CompNociosphere.jobString>
  <!-- EN: Nociosphere departed -->
  <Nociosphere.comps.CompNociosphere.leftLetterLabel>苦痛之球已离开</Nociosphere.comps.CompNociosphere.leftLetterLabel>
  <!-- EN: The nociosphere has disappeared, ending its onslaught.\n\nIt's unclear where the nociosphere has gone or if it will return. -->
  <Nociosphere.comps.CompNociosphere.leftLetterText>苦痛之球终止了攻击并消失得无影无踪。\n\n目前还不清楚苦痛之球去了哪里，是否还会回来。</Nociosphere.comps.CompNociosphere.leftLetterText>
  <!-- EN: Nociosphere onslaught cooldown -->
  <Nociosphere.comps.CompNociosphere.onCooldownString>苦痛之球攻击冷却</Nociosphere.comps.CompNociosphere.onCooldownString>
  <!-- EN: The nociosphere has ended its onslaught and has returned to its initial location. -->
  <Nociosphere.comps.CompNociosphere.onslaughtEndedMessage>苦痛之球停止了攻击并返回了其出发地。</Nociosphere.comps.CompNociosphere.onslaughtEndedMessage>
  <!-- EN: Onslaught mode: {0} seconds left -->
  <Nociosphere.comps.CompNociosphere.onslaughtInspectText>攻击模式：剩余{0}秒</Nociosphere.comps.CompNociosphere.onslaughtInspectText>
  <!-- EN: Unstable: cannot be suppressed -->
  <Nociosphere.comps.CompNociosphere.unstableInspectText>失控：无法被抑制</Nociosphere.comps.CompNociosphere.unstableInspectText>
  <!-- EN: Warning: the nociosphere will resist suppression in {0} days. -->
  <Nociosphere.comps.CompNociosphere.unstableWarning>警告：苦痛之球将在{0}天后抵抗抑制。</Nociosphere.comps.CompNociosphere.unstableWarning>
  
