  <!-- EN: revenant -->
  <Revenant.label>幽魂</Revenant.label>
  <!-- EN: A spindly figure of desiccated skin stretched over an impossibly tall humanoid frame. The revenant's name comes from its pattern of returning to hypnotize new people each night.\n\nOutlander folklore describes an invisible spectre that captures the minds of sinners, placing them in a living hell. In the story, the victims can only be returned to life by hunting the creature as it sleeps and killing it.\n\nA hidden revenant can be revealed with disruptor flares, explosives, EMP, firefoam, or fire. -->
  <Revenant.description>骨瘦如柴的细长鬼影，干瘪的皮肤包裹着高得不可思议的人形骨架。幽魂的名字源于它每晚都会回来寻找新的受害者进行催眠。\n\n外来者的民间传说将其描绘成了一个无形的幽灵，它能够捕获罪人的意识，并将他们带去生不如死的地狱。在传说中，只有在这只怪物沉睡时消灭它，受害者才能起死回生。\n\n可利用眩光信号弹、爆炸物、EMP脉冲、阻燃泡沫或者火焰使其现形。</Revenant.description>
  <!-- EN: head -->
  <Revenant.tools.head.label>头部</Revenant.tools.head.label>
  
  <!-- EN: sightstealer -->
  <Sightstealer.label>隐形魔</Sightstealer.label>
  <!-- EN: Emaciated and misshapen humanoids. Their arms end in sharp, curled claws formed from bioferrite. Sightstealers are fragile, but use psychic influence to render themselves invisible until they get close to their victims. They are known to emit haunting screams as they gather on their terrible hunts. -->
  <Sightstealer.description>瘦削畸形的类人生物。其手臂末端是由活铁构成的弯曲利爪。隐形魔的肉体很脆弱，但它们会利用灵能使自己隐形并偷偷接近受害者。根据对其习性的了解，那毛骨悚然的嚎叫声，便是它们聚集起来进行可怕狩猎的标志。</Sightstealer.description>
